@startuml
title analysis-video - AWS Lambda 4 종 (영상/오디오/프레임/음성지표 후처리)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #FB8C00
}
skinparam component<<storage>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}
skinparam component<<layer>> {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9C4
  BorderColor #FBC02D
}
skinparam component<<face>> {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}

database "S3\nvideo-files (.webm)" as S3In <<storage>>
component "SNS\nvideo-uploaded" as SNS
component "SQS Fan-out\n(converter · frame · audio +\n각자 DLQ)" as SQS
queue "SQS\nvideo-step-complete" as SQSDone
component "face-analyzer Lambda\n(invoke)" as FA <<face>>
component "Backend SQS Worker\n(kombu polling)" as BE <<external>>

package "analysis-video/" {
  package "layers/" {
    component "mefit-video-common\n(config · s3_client\nffmpeg_runner · logger\nevent_parser)" as Lcommon <<layer>>
    component "mefit-ffmpeg-binary\n(static ffmpeg)" as Lffmpeg <<layer>>
    component "audio-analysis\n(librosa · numpy)" as Laudio <<layer>>
  }

  package "functions/" {
    component "video_converter\n.webm → .mp4 (720p H.264)\nmem=1024MB · timeout=5m" as F1
    component "frame_extractor\n.webm → .jpg 1FPS ZIP\nmem=512MB · timeout=3m" as F2
    component "audio_extractor\n.webm → .wav (원본)\n+ .wav 16kHz mono\nmem=512MB · timeout=2m" as F3
    component "voice_analyzer\n.wav → JSON\n(속도 · 필러 · 침묵 · 음량)\nmem=1024MB · timeout=2m" as F4
  }
}

database "S3 scaled-video-files" as S3Mp4 <<storage>>
database "S3 video-frame-files" as S3Jpg <<storage>>
database "S3 audio-files" as S3Wav <<storage>>
database "S3 scaled-audio-files\n(16kHz mono)" as S3Wav16 <<storage>>

S3In --> SNS : ObjectCreated event
SNS --> SQS : subscribe (fan-out)
SQS --> F1 : event source mapping
SQS --> F2
SQS --> F3
SQSDone --> BE : long polling

F1 ..> Lcommon
F1 ..> Lffmpeg
F2 ..> Lcommon
F2 ..> Lffmpeg
F3 ..> Lcommon
F3 ..> Lffmpeg
F4 ..> Lcommon
F4 ..> Laudio

F1 --> S3Mp4 : PUT
F1 --> SQSDone : step=converter
F2 --> S3Jpg : PUT (1FPS .jpg)
F2 --> FA : SQS face-trigger\n(frame 추출 완료 시\nSendMessage)
F2 --> SQSDone : step=frame_extractor
F3 --> S3Wav : PUT
F3 --> S3Wav16 : PUT
F3 --> SQSDone : step=audio

F4 <-- S3Wav16 : 별도 호출 시 GET
note right of F4
  voice_analyzer 는 SNS 트리거가 아닌
  interview-analysis-report Worker 가
  boto3.invoke (RequestResponse) 로 동기 호출
end note

footer analysis-video/ — 4 Lambda · 3 Lambda Layers · ffmpeg + librosa · DLQ 1:1 격리
@enduml
